00:50:59,770 --> 00:51:01,635
Where are you?

756
00:51:01,672 --> 00:51:03,230
I don't- hold on.

757
00:51:09,680 --> 00:51:11,204
Um...

758
00:51:11,248 --> 00:51:13,341
I'm in the morgue.

759
00:51:13,384 --> 00:51:15,852
- Can you get down here?
