976
01:11:12,682 --> 01:11:15,708
The transfer.

977
01:11:15,751 --> 01:11:18,481
You know they were talking
about the transfer?

978
01:11:18,521 --> 01:11:20,648
Yeah, what about it?

979
01:11:20,690 --> 01:11:22,317
It's still pending.

980
01:11:22,358 --> 01:11:25,759
Really? You pulling another one
of your tiger moves?

981
01:11:25,795 --> 01:11:28,320
- Is that it?
- I could take that money

982
01:11:28,364 --> 01:11:30,491
and I could transfer it
right into your account

983
01:11:30,533 --> 01:11:32,501
