And I know your breath.

1006
01:13:44,233 --> 01:13:47,031
Where's Holloway?

1007
01:13:47,069 --> 01:13:50,869
You didn't kill
Holloway, did you?

1008
01:13:50,906 --> 01:13:54,433
I didn't know
you had it in you.

1009
01:13:54,477 --> 01:13:56,536
Mary.

1010
01:13:56,579 --> 01:13:58,240
Mary, listen to me.

1011
01:13:58,280 --> 01:14:00,646
I'm coming for you, Mary.
I'm coming down there.

1012
01:14:00,683 --> 01:14:03,174
You just stay put, sweets.
We can sort this all out.

1013
01:14:03,219 --> 01:14:05,380
I'm coming for you.
Damn it!

1014
01:14:05,421 --> 01:14:07,912
Holloway screwed up.
She's not dead.

1015
01:14:07,957 --> 01:14:11,085
Just relax. I'll get the money, okay?
We'll get the money!

1016
01:14:11,127 --> 01:14:13,095
I thought you said
you knew this chick, Steve.

1017
01:14:13,129 --> 01:14:16,064
I do. I told you, she's smart.

1018
01:14:16,098 --> 01:14:19,556
- Hello.
- Barry: I'm afraid there's been a problem.

1019
01:14:19,602 --> 01:14:21,092
The wire's
been reversed.

1020
01:14:21,137 --> 01:14:22,502
Cooper:
What are you talking about?

1021
01:14:22,538 --> 01:14:24,506
The bank recalled
the money.

1022
01:14:24,540 --> 01:14:26,872
Can't do that.

1023
01:14:26,909 --> 01:14:29,400
- It's not my call, sir.
- That's not good enough.

1024
01:14:29,445 --> 01:14:31,709
Sir, there's nothing more
that I can do, okay?

1025
01:14:31,747 --> 01:14:34,682
It's not on my end.
I did what you told me to do.

1026
01:14:34,717 --> 01:14:37,447
- I did what you asked me to do.
- I'll get them to rescind it.

1027
01:14:37,486 --> 01:14:39,613
Sir, do whatever
you have to do, sir.

1028
01:14:39,655 --> 01:14:42,647
I'm sorry.

1029
01:14:44,293 --> 01:14:47,160
We gotta go back.
Get us back to the hospital.

1030
01:14:47,196 --> 01:14:49,630
I'll take care
of it myself.

1031
01:14:49,665 --> 01:14:52,657
I'll put a bullet
in her head right now.

1032
01:14:52,701 --> 01:14:54,794
Turn around here.

1033
01:14:56,672 --> 01:14:58,640
Son of a bitch!

1034
01:15:28,571 --> 01:15:30,198
There she is!

1035
01:16:03,439 --> 01:16:05,737
End of the road, baby.

1036
01:16:05,774 --> 01:16:08,766
All right, you take the wheel.
Meet us topside.

1037
01:16:20,556 --> 01:16:23,286
Woman:
All units, three armed suspects

1038
01:16:23,325 --> 01:16:25,885
spotted in hospital parking garage
driving silver sedan.

1039
01:16:25,928 --> 01:16:28,624
All units respond.

1040
01:16:39,942 --> 01:16:43,309
Shh shh shh.
Wait wait.

1041
01:17:07,937 --> 01:17:09,734
- Where'd they go?
- I don't know.

1042
01:17:09,772 --> 01:17:12,002
- Where'd they go?
- They went that way.

1043
01:17:12,041 --> 01:17:14,771
- Chill out!
- You stay right here.

1044
01:17:14,810 --> 01:17:15,868
You hear me?
Right here!

1045
01:17:20,115 --> 01:17:22,743
I need backup
at County Hospital now.

1046
01:17:22,785 --> 01:17:25,652
Mary honey,
I'm not gonna hurt you.

1047
01:17:55,484 --> 01:17:58,078
Mare bear.

1048
01:18:03,058 --> 01:18:06,118
No! No, don't hit her.
We need her information.

1049
01:18:06,161 --> 01:18:08,891
Honey, Mary.
He's sorry.

1050
01:18:15,337 --> 01:18:17,328
Mare.

1051
01:18:54,643 --> 01:18:56,076
Mary: Please stop!

1052
01:18:56,111 --> 01:18:59,342
Cooper, put the gun down.

1053
01:18:59,381 --> 01:19:01,576
You're a smart girl,
Walsh.

1054
01:19:01,617 --> 01:19:04,450
There's no good way out of this.
Don't be stupid.

1055
01:19:04,486 --> 01:19:07,455
I'm gonna put my gun down.

1056
01:19:07,489 --> 01:19:09,286
I'm gonna do it
right here.

1057
01:19:09,324 --> 01:19:12,760
I'll go my way.
You go yours, okay?

1058
01:19:14,329 --> 01:19:16,797
Drop your weapon,
Cooper.

1059
01:19:25,140 --> 01:19:28,473
Coop...

1060
01:19:28,510 --> 01:19:30,501
you okay?

1061
01:19:50,732 --> 01:19:53,257
Kevin:
Whoa whoa whoa!

1062
01:19:53,302 --> 01:19:55,270
Where'd you get a gun,
honey?

1063
01:19:55,304 --> 01:19:57,329
Put it away.
Stay where you are.

1064
01:19:57,372 --> 01:20:01,240
Whoa whoa whoa.
Baby, I'll put this away.

1065
01:20:01,276 --> 01:20:03,608
Take it easy.

1066
01:20:03,645 --> 01:20:07,081
This is a whole
different side of you

1067
01:20:07,116 --> 01:20:08,947
I've never seen.

1068
01:20:08,984 --> 01:20:12,476
And how do you feel
about that side?

1069
01:20:12,521 --> 01:20:14,955
I like it.

1070
01:20:14,990 --> 01:20:16,924
I like it a lot.

1071
01:20:16,959 --> 01:20:19,427
Me too.

1072
01:20:19,461 --> 01:20:22,430
Baby, this whole thing
has gotten completely

1073
01:20:22,464 --> 01:20:24,261
out of hand.

1074
01:20:24,299 --> 01:20:25,994
You were never
supposed to get hurt.

1075
01:20:26,034 --> 01:20:28,025
Okay?

1076
01:20:28,070 --> 01:20:30,334
Look,
we can work this out.

1077
01:20:30,372 --> 01:20:33,535
Okay, listen,

1078
01:20:33,575 --> 01:20:36,942
forget these guys, okay?

1079
01:20:36,979 --> 01:20:40,210
Why don't you and I
just take the money?

1080
01:20:40,249 --> 01:20:41,978
You can resend it.

1081
01:20:42,017 --> 01:20:45,009
We'll take it. We can be anybody
we wanna be.

1082
01:20:45,053 --> 01:20:48,420
We can go anywhere we wanna go.
Think about that.

1083
01:20:50,692 --> 01:20:53,786
No no no,
it started off about money,

1084
01:20:53,829 --> 01:20:56,389
but now, I mean,

1085
01:20:56,431 --> 01:20:58,194
honey,
everything's changed.

1086
01:20:58,233 --> 01:21:01,361
I would hate for you

1087
01:21:01,403 --> 01:21:04,770
to see four months

1088
01:21:04,806 --> 01:21:07,604
of wasted time
and effort.

1089
01:21:07,643 --> 01:21:09,577
I would really hate it.

1090
01:21:09,611 --> 01:21:10,805
It would hurt me.

1091
01:21:10,846 --> 01:21:12,837
Yeah, that's what
I'm saying.

1092
01:21:12,881 --> 01:21:15,042
So you and I, we could take
the money together.

1093
01:21:15,083 --> 01:21:19,019
Right here.

1094
01:21:19,054 --> 01:21:21,215
And it could happen
just with the push of a little button.

1095
01:21:21,256 --> 01:21:23,087
We can go
anywhere we want to.

1096
01:21:23,125 --> 01:21:26,026
We can be anybody
we want to.

1097
01:21:26,061 --> 01:21:27,926
Think about it.

1098
01:21:27,963 --> 01:21:31,865
Baby, that sounds
pretty fantastic.

1099
01:21:31,900 --> 01:21:33,765
You...

1100
01:21:33,802 --> 01:21:35,997
always told me
I was priceless.

1101
01:21:36,038 --> 01:21:38,973
Baby, you are priceless...

1102
01:21:39,007 --> 01:21:40,838
to me.

1103
01:21:40,876 --> 01:21:43,242
Just didn't know

1104
01:21:43,278 --> 01:21:45,542
that I was
a $10 million catch!

1105
01:21:45,581 --> 01:21:47,742
No!

1106
01:21:50,285 --> 01:21:52,276
Mary.

1107
01:21:53,822 --> 01:21:56,791
See now, I'm gonna have
to break up with you.

1108
01:21:56,825 --> 01:21:58,258
For real!

1109
01:22:05,267 --> 01:22:07,258
Mare!

1110
01:22:17,579 --> 01:22:19,809
Mary.
Mary, don't move.

1111
01:22:19,848 --> 01:22:21,543
Stay right there!
Don't move.

1112
01:22:21,583 --> 01:22:24,074
I'm gonna come to you.
You're okay.

1113
01:22:24,119 --> 01:22:26,110
Stay right there.

1114
01:22:48,844 --> 01:22:50,835
Okay.

1115
01:22:54,149 --> 01:22:56,140
I'm sorry.

1116
01:22:58,453 --> 01:23:00,444
Thank you.

1117
01:23:40,662 --> 01:23:43,062
- Detective Franklin.
- Mm-hmm.

1118
01:23:43,098 --> 01:23:46,864
Before we go up there

1119
01:23:46,902 --> 01:23:49,268
and see all those people,

1120
01:23:49,304 --> 01:23:51,636
I just wanted to ask,

1121
01:23:51,673 --> 01:23:53,664
why did you believe me?

1122
01:23:57,012 --> 01:23:59,412
This.

1123
01:23:59,448 --> 01:24:01,541
You left it in the chapel.

1124
01:24:01,583 --> 01:24:03,244
What about this?

1125
01:24:03,285 --> 01:24:05,753
The last chapter.
Take a look.

1126
01:24:12,027 --> 01:24:14,723
The whole thing,
it's right there.

1127
01:24:28,410 --> 01:24:31,538
Couldn't even come up
with something original.

1128
01:24:34,182 --> 01:24:37,310
Why don't you keep this
for evidence?

1129
01:24:37,352 --> 01:24:40,879
- You gonna be okay?
- Sure I am.

1130
01:24:40,922 --> 01:24:43,755
Gonna just keep on living

1131
01:24:43,792 --> 01:24:46,022
one day at a time.

1132
01:24:46,061 --> 01:24:49,292
- How about you?
- I called my wife.

1133
01:24:49,331 --> 01:24:52,061
- You did?
- You got me thinking.

1134
01:24:52,100 --> 01:24:54,967
Maybe I let her go
too easily.

1135
01:24:55,003 --> 01:24:58,439
I am proud of you, kid.

1136
01:24:58,473 --> 01:25:01,067
Come on. Let's get you
to a real hospital.

1137
01:25:01,109 --> 01:25:05,045
- Okay?
- Then the games can really begin.

